  <h2>Pro Tips for Better TTS Results</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Use punctuation</strong> — Our tool reads based on punctuation. Proper periods and commas = natural pacing.</li>
    <li><strong>Add emphasis with caps</strong> — IMPORTANT words in CAPS are often read with more emphasis.</li>
    <li><strong>Adjust speed for complex content</strong> — Slow down (0.75x) for technical text. Speed up (1.5x) for casual reading.</li>
    <li><strong>Try different voices</strong> — Every voice has different qualities. Experiment to find what works for your content.</li>
    <li><strong>Record while listening</strong> — Use Win+G (Windows) or QuickTime (Mac) to capture audio for later use.</li>
  </ul>

